nattelf 142243427598 "2016-04-04 16:21:29 GMT" https://nattelf.tumblr.com/post/142243427598/3-ways-to-keep-yourself-safe-when-youre-not-ready "runonsentencesaboutemotions:  revolutionarykoolaid:  misssatori:  ask-an-mra-anything:  ask-an-mra-anything:  hellyeahscarleteen: In addition to what’s mentioned in this link
column2: we have some info to help folks make a plan to stay safe when leaving an abusive relationship
column3: and when they can’t leave just yet: The Scarleteen Safety Plan Seriously
column4: I’ve only been able to skim this article so far
column5: but I definitely plan on reading the whole thing later  If you’re being abused by your partner
column6: and you’re reading this right now
column7: then you have awe-inspiring strength. You’re suffering
column8: but you have the courage to seek out ideas on how to take care of yourself. I’m guessing you haven’t come across many tips like these. When I was being abused
column9: the only advice I found was about how to leave an abusive partner
column10: or how to heal after you’ve left.  In this society we sometimes talk about abuse victims being strong after they leave
column11: but frame them as weak before hand. I think that is so wrong. Living in an abusive relationship takes a strength that most people cannot even comprehend. you’re not weak because you stay. there are a million reasons why we stay because
column13: abusers actively work to keep their victims trapped.  So know that if you’re in an abusive relationship right now as you read this
column14: I think you are strong as fuck
column15: and I am rooting hard as hell for you.   Honestly
column16: if people feel even a little inclined to reblog this
column17: I would appreciate it. I am not trying to guilt anyone
column18: if you don’t reblog I won’t think you’re a horrible person
column19: that’s totally your prerogative… But if these words can help even just one current victim of domestic violence… I would be so happy.   So many people can’t leave. So many. Please be safe.  SIGNAL BOOST  For anyone who needs it " False link
